Chapter 369: Out of Danger
The situation was overwhelmingly one-sided, with both sides firing with all their might, filling the entire sky above the ocean with smoke and gunpowder.
Bai Ye once again fired the high-speed magnetic wave scanning gun in his hand, smashing another plane, the gun was really handy, he was getting addicted to using it, Xiao Naibao commanded calmly, the air force of the first terrorist organization formed an invincible offensive and defensive team, starting the final round of fierce attacks.
Seeing the situation was not good, Nickla, disregarding etiquette, raised his voice, "Master, let's retreat. If we continue like this, we will be completely wiped out."
Louis clenched his fists tightly, his face covered in gloom, full of hostility, he could clearly see the current situation.
But he was unwilling to accept being driven back like this, they were so close, he could have captured them again, it was really frustrating.
The man's emerald green eyes, with a glimpse of killing intent, then hidden in those silent and melancholic eyes, nodded towards Nickla, immediately ordering to cover and retreat.
Louis gazed at the two figures drifting in the sky above the sea, snorted coldly, this time they were lucky, he wouldn't let it go just like that.
