Xiao Naibao also smiled elegantly, ordered to stop the attack, a calmness filled his pitch-black eyes, and he slowly said, "Not pursuing, letting him die like this would be too much of a pity, the cat and mouse game has just begun."
This game has already turned the tables.
Louis, he should never have, absolutely should not have provoked him, Nono's death, he must find someone to accompany her in burial, otherwise he will not be able to swallow this anger.
When the game starts, Louis calls the shots, but...
Xiao Naibao's smile was cold and sharp, imposing and intimidating. When it comes to when it will end, he has the final say.
Bai Ye smiled, casually brushed his sleeves, "Alright, let's not pursue, we have plenty of capital to play with him. Maybe they won't even have a chance to act, Louis will have someone rushing to deal with him."
Xiao Naibao watched the direction they were escaping in, coldly smiling without saying a word.
"Chu Li, it's over, no need for support, let's go back immediately."
Bai Ye and Chu Li ordered their subordinates to turn back to Rome after a phone call.
It took a tremendous amount of effort for Heiying and the others to drag Ye Sanshao and Cheng Anya up, they all knew that Cheng Anya had a virus on her, so they had taken protective measures early on, Ye Sanshao also warned them that he had a virus on him, making Heiying and the others even more cautious.
